Package: rcdf
Type: Package
Title: A comprehensive toolkit for working with RCDF (Encrypted Parquet) files in R. 
Version: 0.1.0
Description: This package provides utilities for reading, writing, and managing RCDF files, including encryption and decryption support. It offers a flexible interface for handling data stored in encrypted Parquet format, along with metadata extraction, key management, and secure operations using AES and RSA encryption.
